transcript: One time the assembly line was not working so I had to fix it and I had to put it back. So the problem was with the ESP32 void so I took it and read the code and I did some testing and I found a bug and then I fixed it and put it back into place. Before putting back into the main circuit I did some testing on a smaller circuit in order not to burn the components but then I put it back into the assembly line and it worked.
